message:
International Justice Mission UMN has their second general meeting TOMORROW MORNING at 11am in Folwell Hall! 
We are a bunch of students passionate about seeking justice for victims of modern day slavery in the name of Christ. Slavery is the daily reality for over 27million people in the world today. The statistics are outrageous and we intend to change them.
Come to our meeting and check us out and see what you can do! Coffee and treats provided. Invite your friends and share this post. Like our page for more info on meetings and upcoming events!
